headline: Here’s How Options Traders Are Betting On Nvidia
summary: Options traders are betting on fireworks after Nvidia's earnings report.  In recent days, some of the most actively-traded Nvidia options contracts were call options pegged to the stock jumping to $190 and $200, according to Cboe Global Markets data.  ?_Read more_ on Nvidia's AI chip business in China.

headline: Cybin Receives Australian Approval for EMBRACE, a Multinational Pivotal Study Evaluating CYB003 for the Adjunctive Treatment of Major Depressive Disorder
